string-array.item:
"1. The application will disable your Wifi/Data Connections
2. Once they are disabled, you can launch WhatsApp by clicking on Launch Whatsapp button.
In order to start WhatsApp without need of clicking button, please check the Auto Start Whatsapp next time checkbox."
